title: Wall Street Breakfast July 14: Celsius Files for Bankruptcy: Crypto Canary or 'Winter' Victim?
author: Seeking Alpha

description: Celsius files for bankruptcy: Crypto canary or 'winter' victim? Netflix announces Microsoft to be its global ad sales, tech partner. S&P, Dow, Nasdaq futures slide with PPI on tap, 100 basis points priced in. Catch today’s WSB article here.
